heading: 2. The 9th day of June 2023 is appointed as the day on which Parts 2 to 9
text_raw:
2. The 9th day of June 2023 is appointed as the day on which Parts 2 to 9 
of the Communications Regulation and Digital Hub Development Agency 
(Amendment) Act 2023 (No. 4 of 2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

6 June, 2023. 

EAMON RYAN, 

Minister for the Environment, Climate and 
Communications. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 13th June, 2023.
